  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    To evaluate this project using the editor:
    
    1. Activate the microphone icon located at the bottom left of the preview window.
    2. After clicking the input mic button on the summary component, play a video or any other audio source, like a podcast, for 1-2 minutes.
    3. Observe as the summary cards populate after approximately 500-600 characters have been processed.
    4. While wearing headphones, press the input mic on the chat component:
    Ask questions related to the summary (using the summary tool).
    Inquire about your surroundings (using the spatial tool).
    Create diagrams (using the diagram tool). 
    To test this project on Spectacles:
    
    Use a loud, high-quality audio source. Note that you might not achieve the same precision as in the editor, particularly with a podcast playing on your laptop. This issue will be addressed in future updates. Watch for the cards as they populate.
    Engage with the chat component just as you did in the editor. 
    For additional information, please refer to the README.md file.
